		<title>禁用 WordPress 4.7 新增的PDF缩略图预览功能</title>
		<link>https://www.wpdaxue.com/disable-pdf-thumbnail-previews-in-wordpress.html</link>
		<comments>https://www.wpdaxue.com/disable-pdf-thumbnail-previews-in-wordpress.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 13 Dec 2016 23:55:39 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[倡萌]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[后台定制]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[PDF]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.wpdaxue.com/?p=42527</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[WordPress 4.7 新增了一个PDF缩略图生成和预览功能，上传PDF文件后，会自动生成这个PDF文件的 &#8230;]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>WordPress 4.7 新增了一个PDF缩略图生成和预览功能，上传PDF文件后，会自动生成这个PDF文件的缩略图，并显示预览，如下图：</p>
<p><img title="20161214074826_wpdaxue_com" style="float: none; margin: 0px auto; display: block" alt="20161214074826_wpdaxue_com" src="https://img.wpdaxue.com/2016/12/20161214074826_wpdaxue_com.png" width="521" height="320"></p>
<p>但是如果你已经在使用其他PDF插件实现了类似的功能，并且不希望与这个新增的功能有冲突，你可能想要禁用掉 WordPress 4.7 新增的PDF缩略图预览功能。实现的方法很简单，在你当前主题的 functions.php 文件添加如下代码即可：</p>
<pre lang="php" escaped="true" line="1">/**
 * Disable PDF Thumbnail Previews in WordPress
 * http://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-disable-pdf-thumbnail-previews-in-wordpress/
 */
function wpb_disable_pdf_previews() {  
    $fallbacksizes = array();  
    return $fallbacksizes;  
}  
add_filter('fallback_intermediate_image_sizes', 'wpb_disable_pdf_previews');</pre>
<p>然后你上传PDF文件后，插入界面如下图所示：</p>
<p><img title="20161214074850_wpdaxue_com" style="float: none; margin: 0px auto; display: block" alt="20161214074850_wpdaxue_com" src="https://img.wpdaxue.com/2016/12/20161214074850_wpdaxue_com.png" width="522" height="308"></p>
<p>参考出自：<a title="http://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-disable-pdf-thumbnail-previews-in-wordpress/" href="http://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-disable-pdf-thumbnail-previews-in-wordpress/" target="_blank">http://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-disable-pdf-thumbnail-previews-in-wordpress/</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
			<wfw:commentRss>https://www.wpdaxue.com/disable-pdf-thumbnail-previews-in-wordpress.html/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
		<slash:comments>2</slash:comments>
